      "seed": 501928150,
      "version": 433,
      "versionNonce": 641444170,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1769799357896,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Q -> How to use middleware?\n\nadd middleware in settings.py inside MIDDLEWARE list\n\n'djmiddleware.middleware.custom_middleware.IPBlockingMiddleware'\n\n\nNow this middleware will be called on every request if IP will be in BlockedIPs then it will return from here only and give response\nForbidden : IP not allowed",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Q -> How to use middleware?\n\nadd middleware in settings.py inside MIDDLEWARE list\n\n'djmiddleware.middleware.custom_middleware.IPBlockingMiddleware'\n\n\nNow this middleware will be called on every request if IP will be in BlockedIPs then it will return from here only and give response\nForbidden : IP not allowed",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
